### 路径转发网关服务测试接口

# 基础URL
@baseURL = http://localhost:18202

### 1. 健康检查
GET {{baseURL}}/gateway/health

### 2. 获取项目列表（路径转发模式）
POST {{baseURL}}/gateway/storage/ListProjects
Content-Type: application/json
X-App-Id: test123
X-App-Key: test123
X-Trace-Id: trace-12345
X-Access-Token: optional_access_token

{}

### 3. 创建项目（路径转发模式）
POST {{baseURL}}/gateway/storage/CreateProject
Content-Type: application/json
X-App-Id: test123
X-App-Key: test123
X-Trace-Id: trace-67890
X-Access-Token: user_access_token

{
  "proj_name": "新项目",
  "remark": "这是一个新项目",
  "dataset": {
    "dataset_name": "主数据集",
    "data_type": 102,
    "time_series_period": "1D",
    "validation_rule": "",
    "remark": "主要数据集"
  },
  "fields": [
    {
      "field_name": "名称",
      "interface_name": "name",
      "desc": "项目名称字段",
      "is_required": true,
      "is_unique": false,
      "is_metadata": false,
      "validation_rule": "",
      "write_example": "示例项目",
      "remark": "项目名称",
      "field_primary_format": 1,
      "field_secondary_format": 0
    }
  ]
}

### 4. 测试其他存储服务接口
POST {{baseURL}}/gateway/storage/GetData
Content-Type: application/json
X-App-Id: test123
X-App-Key: test123
X-Trace-Id: trace-get-data

{
  "project_id": 1,
  "dataset_id": 101,
  "object_id": "BTCUSDT",
  "freq": "1H"
}

### 5. 测试认证服务接口
POST {{baseURL}}/gateway/auth/Login
Content-Type: application/json
X-App-Id: test123
X-App-Key: test123
X-Trace-Id: trace-auth-login

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password_hash": "hashed_password",
  "device_id": "device123"
}

### 6. 测试缺少必要头部信息
POST {{baseURL}}/gateway/storage/ListProjects
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 7. 测试缺少App-Key
POST {{baseURL}}/gateway/storage/ListProjects
Content-Type: application/json
X-App-Id: test123

{}

### 8. 测试未知服务
POST {{baseURL}}/gateway/unknown_service/SomeMethod
Content-Type: application/json
X-App-Id: test123
X-App-Key: test123
X-Trace-Id: trace-unknown

{}

### 9. 测试GET请求
GET {{baseURL}}/gateway/storage/ListProjects?project_id=1
X-App-Id: test123
X-App-Key: test123
X-Trace-Id: trace-get-request

### 10. 测试带复杂参数的请求
POST {{baseURL}}/gateway/storage/UpdateProject
Content-Type: application/json
X-App-Id: test123
X-App-Key: test123
X-Trace-Id: trace-update-project
X-Client-Ip: 192.168.1.100

{
  "proj_id": 1,
  "remark": "更新后的项目备注信息"
} 